<%- include('partials/header') %>

<style>
  .features-hero {
    min-height: 180px;
    display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; text-align: center;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(233,69,96,0.08), rgba(212,175,55,0.06));
    border-radius: var(--radius-lg); margin-bottom: 36px; padding: 36px 20px;
    border: 1px solid rgba(233,69,96,0.1);
  }
  .features-hero h1 { color: var(--text); font-size: 2rem; margin-bottom: 6px; }
  .features-hero p { color: var(--light); font-size: 1rem; }
  .section-label { color: var(--primary); font-weight: 700; font-size: 0.85rem; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 1.5px; margin-bottom: 8px; }
  .section-heading { font-size: 1.4rem; margin-bottom: 6px; color: var(--text); }
  .section-desc { color: var(--light); margin-bottom: 24px; font-size: 0.95rem; }
  .feat-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fill, minmax(260px, 1fr)); gap: 18px; margin-bottom: 40px; }
  .feat-card {
    background: var(--card-bg); border: var(--card-border); border-radius: var(--radius); padding: 24px;
    transition: all 0.25s ease; position: relative; overflow: hidden;
  }
  .feat-card:hover { transform: translateY(-3px); box-shadow: var(--shadow-md); border-color: var(--primary); }
  .feat-card::before {
    content: ''; position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; right: 0; height: 3px;
    background: linear-gradient(90deg, var(--primary), var(--gold-light));
    transform: scaleX(0); transform-origin: left; transition: transform 0.3s ease;
  }
  .feat-card:hover::before { transform: scaleX(1); }
  .feat-icon { font-size: 2rem; margin-bottom: 10px; display: block; }
  .feat-card h3 { font-size: 1.05rem; margin-bottom: 8px; color: var(--text); }
  .feat-card p { color: var(--light); font-size: 0.9rem; line-height: 1.6; margin: 0; }
  .feat-tag { display: inline-block; padding: 2px 10px; border-radius: 20px; font-size: 0.72rem; background: rgba(233,69,96,0.08); color: var(--primary); margin-top: 10px; }
</style>

<div class="features-hero">
  <div>
    <h1>旅途笔记 · 功能亮点</h1>
    <p>基于 Node.js + Express + MongoDB 的全功能旅游社交平台</p>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="section-label">核心架构</div>
<div class="section-heading">稳定可靠的技术地基</div>
<div class="section-desc">MVC 分层 + ODM 建模 + 中间件鉴权</div>
<div class="feat-grid">
  <div class="feat-card"><span class="feat-icon">🛢️</span><h3>MongoDB + Mongoose</h3><p>ODM 定义 User/Travel/Comment/Notification 四模型，关联查询自动填充，密码 pre-save 加密。</p><span class="feat-tag">数据层</span></div>
  <div class="feat-card"><span class="feat-icon">🧩</span><h3>MVC 分层架构</h3><p>模型-视图-控制器清晰分离，路由与业务逻辑独立，EJS 模板动态渲染全部页面。</p><span class="feat-tag">架构</span></div>
  <div class="feat-card"><span class="feat-icon">🔐</span><h3>注册登录鉴权</h3><p>bcrypt 哈希加密密码，express-session 持久化登录，全局中间件注入用户信息与未读通知。</p><span class="feat-tag">安全</span></div>
  <div class="feat-card"><span class="feat-icon">🔍</span><h3>全文模糊搜索</h3><p>MongoDB $regex 匹配标题与目的地，结果页继承首页布局，支持分页浏览。</p><span class="feat-tag">搜索</span></div>
</div>

<div class="section-label">内容创作</div>
<div class="section-heading">记录每一段旅程</div>
<div class="section-desc">富文本 + 多图上传 + 分类管理</div>
<div class="feat-grid">
  <div class="feat-card"><span class="feat-icon">✍️</span><h3>Quill 富文本编辑器</h3><p>支持加粗、斜体、标题、列表，编辑时完美回显，兼容服务端存储。</p><span class="feat-tag">编辑器</span></div>
  <div class="feat-card"><span class="feat-icon">📸</span><h3>Multer 多图上传</h3><p>封面图 + 画廊多图分字段处理，编辑时可预览与替换，自动创建上传目录。</p><span class="feat-tag">文件</span></div>
  <div class="feat-card"><span class="feat-icon">🖼️</span><h3>图片画廊展示</h3><p>详情页网格画廊 + 悬停缩放，点击跳转原图，全方位展示旅行画面。</p><span class="feat-tag">展示</span></div>
  <div class="feat-card"><span class="feat-icon">🏷️</span><h3>分类标签体系</h3><p>自然风光/城市漫步/美食之旅/历史文化，发布选择，搜索过滤。</p><span class="feat-tag">分类</span></div>
</div>

<div class="section-label">社交互动</div>
<div class="section-heading">分享与交流</div>
<div class="section-desc">点赞 · 评论 · 收藏 · 通知</div>
<div class="feat-grid">
  <div class="feat-card"><span class="feat-icon">❤️</span><h3>Toggle 点赞</h3><p>数组存储用户 ID，前后端联动判断已点赞状态，按钮即时切换样式。</p><span class="feat-tag">互动</span></div>
  <div class="feat-card"><span class="feat-icon">💬</span><h3>评论系统</h3><p>独立 Comment 模型关联游记与用户，发表后实时刷新，自动通知游记作者。</p><span class="feat-tag">互动</span></div>
  <div class="feat-card"><span class="feat-icon">⭐</span><h3>收藏夹</h3><p>用户模型内嵌收藏数组，个人中心分「我的游记」与「我的收藏」双面板展示。</p><span class="feat-tag">互动</span></div>
  <div class="feat-card"><span class="feat-icon">🔔</span><h3>站内通知</h3><p>点赞/评论即时推送，导航栏未读计数徽标，一键全部已读，EMOJI 类型区分。</p><span class="feat-tag">互动</span></div>
  <div class="feat-card"><span class="feat-icon">👤</span><h3>个人主页</h3><p>公开展示头像、简介、游记列表、收藏列表，点击作者名即可访问。</p><span class="feat-tag">用户</span></div>
  <div class="feat-card"><span class="feat-icon">⚙️</span><h3>资料编辑</h3><p>支持修改头像（文件上传）、个人简介，实时保存全局生效。</p><span class="feat-tag">用户</span></div>
</div>

<div class="section-label">界面体验</div>
<div class="section-heading">从内到外的优雅</div>
<div class="section-desc">Glassmorphism + 响应式 + 动画系统</div>
<div class="feat-grid">
  <div class="feat-card"><span class="feat-icon">🪟</span><h3>Glassmorphism 风格</h3><p>backdrop-filter 毛玻璃模糊 + rgba 半透明卡片 + 柔和阴影系统，全站统一视觉。</p><span class="feat-tag">UI</span></div>
  <div class="feat-card"><span class="feat-icon">🌄</span><h3>全屏固定背景 + 轮播</h3><p>沉浸式大图背景滚动固定，管理员可配置轮播/静止模式与图片选择。</p><span class="feat-tag">UI</span></div>
  <div class="feat-card"><span class="feat-icon">📱</span><h3>三端响应式</h3><p>1024px 平板 / 768px 手机横屏 / 480px 手机竖屏，Flexbox+Grid 自适应。</p><span class="feat-tag">UI</span></div>
  <div class="feat-card"><span class="feat-icon">✨</span><h3>滚动动画系统</h3><p>IntersectionObserver 监听元素可见性，CSS fade-in-up + 错位延迟序列。</p><span class="feat-tag">UI</span></div>
  <div class="feat-card"><span class="feat-icon">🗺️</span><h3>Leaflet.js 交互地图</h3><p>Nominatim 地理编码自动定位目的地，标记弹窗展示位置信息。</p><span class="feat-tag">UI</span></div>
  <div class="feat-card"><span class="feat-icon">📄</span><h3>服务端分页</h3><p>skip/limit 每页 12 条可配置，页码导航栏替代无限滚动，体验流畅。</p><span class="feat-tag">UI</span></div>
  <div class="feat-card"><span class="feat-icon">⬆️</span><h3>回到顶部</h3><p>右下角固定按钮，滚动超过一屏显示，平滑返回顶部。</p><span class="feat-tag">UI</span></div>
  <div class="feat-card"><span class="feat-icon">☁️</span><h3>Railway 云部署</h3><p>GitHub 自动部署，MONGODB_URI 环境变量注入，自动健康检查与崩溃重启。</p><span class="feat-tag">运维</span></div>
</div>

<%- include('partials/footer') %>
